Ariel Investment Trust - Ariel Fund: Private Company Information - Bloomberg










































  





















































































July 25, 2017 5:12 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Ariel Investment Trust - Ariel Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Ariel Investment Trust - Ariel Fund is an open ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Ariel Investments, LLC. The fund invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund primarily invests in value stocks of small cap and mid cap companies with a market capitalization between $1 billion and $7.5 billion. It employs fundamental analysis by focusing on factors such as capital appreciation over time, high barriers to entry, sustainable competitive advantages, predictable fundamentals that allow for double-digit earnings growth, skilled management teams, and solid financials to create its portfolio....
Ariel Investment Trust - Ariel Fund is an open ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Ariel Investments, LLC. The fund invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund primarily invests in value stocks of small cap and mid cap companies with a market capitalization between $1 billion and $7.5 billion. It employs fundamental analysis by focusing on factors such as capital appreciation over time, high barriers to entry, sustainable competitive advantages, predictable fundamentals that allow for double-digit earnings growth, skilled management teams, and solid financials to create its portfolio. The fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the Russell 2500 Value Index, Russell 2500 Index, and S&P 500 Index. It employs proprietary research to create its portfolio. The fund does not invest in corporations whose primary source of revenue is derived from the production or sale of tobacco products or the manufacture of handguns. Ariel Investment Trust - Ariel Fund was formed on November 6, 1986 and is domiciled in the United States.
